column8: The Space Needle is an observation tower in Seattle; Washington. Six parachutists have leaped from the tower since its opening; but this activity is only legal with prior consent. Four jumpers were part of various promotions; and the other two were arrested.)

Tourism is an important part of the Hawaii economy. The summer months and major holidays are the most popular times for outsiders to visit; however; especially when residents of the rest of the United States are looking to escape from cold; winter weather. The Japanese are also principal tourists.)

MobiSys seeks to present innovative and significant research on the design; implementation; usage; and evaluation of mobile computing and wireless systems; applications; and services. This conference builds on the success of the previous twelve MobiSys conferences. It will be held in Florence; Italy; in May.)
